  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/b04eebc402de61c1ae384477279c8119.avif?t=1692380437\" width=600 height=230 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/edec52e879cb96072119e2b0278f4a09.webp?t=1692380437\" width=600 height=47 /></span><br><br><strong>WELCOME CAMPERS! DEATH GIVES YOU A SECOND CHANCE</strong><br><br>Survive the hill now saves players from some troubles with its updated content in the full version.<br>and will offer some more action content to the survivors.<br><br><strong>Full Release notes and more..</strong><br><br><br>New and main mission change in the game:<br><br>Try to escape from the two exit points on the map.<br>Blow up the barriers here with the dynamite you collect.<br>Before you can collect dynamite, you need to bypass the System by playing the mini-game available in Hut Shelters, after which the storages are unlocked.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/ad1f040553770cf2e142c039495ff040.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/ad1f040553770cf2e142c039495ff040.webm?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/ad1f040553770cf2e142c039495ff040.mp4?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/e656fec65a32ff948b9013c4f030f3e6.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/e656fec65a32ff948b9013c4f030f3e6.webm?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/e656fec65a32ff948b9013c4f030f3e6.mp4?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/0bf29cc0b593c4237d6aa98a07f74dbc.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/0bf29cc0b593c4237d6aa98a07f74dbc.webm?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/0bf29cc0b593c4237d6aa98a07f74dbc.mp4?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>You will face a new zombie attack every time you unlock it.<br>and this process will turn into an increasingly difficult chaos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/7777d5d676e9e8404599a7a946dd2eca.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/7777d5d676e9e8404599a7a946dd2eca.webm?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/7777d5d676e9e8404599a7a946dd2eca.mp4?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Newly added weapons and ammo storages.<br><br>A new type of dismembered zombies.<br><br>The killer clown's evolving abilities will make it harder for the survivors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/80b122bba07af158329c96f7b6e61ef4.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/80b122bba07af158329c96f7b6e61ef4.webm?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/80b122bba07af158329c96f7b6e61ef4.mp4?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each time the killer clown dies or kills a survivor, he gains an increasing defense and damage buff.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/01840186946ec16678ca071e68c4db7a.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/01840186946ec16678ca071e68c4db7a.webm?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/01840186946ec16678ca071e68c4db7a.mp4?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Optimization improvements, fixed drop issues and renewed lightings and more.. Updated full version in V2.00",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/b04eebc402de61c1ae384477279c8119.avif?t=1692380437\" width=600 height=230 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/edec52e879cb96072119e2b0278f4a09.webp?t=1692380437\" width=600 height=47 /></span><br><br><strong>WELCOME CAMPERS! DEATH GIVES YOU A SECOND CHANCE</strong><br><br>Survive the hill now saves players from some troubles with its updated content in the full version.<br>and will offer some more action content to the survivors.<br><br><strong>Full Release notes and more..</strong><br><br><br>New and main mission change in the game:<br><br>Try to escape from the two exit points on the map.<br>Blow up the barriers here with the dynamite you collect.<br>Before you can collect dynamite, you need to bypass the System by playing the mini-game available in Hut Shelters, after which the storages are unlocked.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/ad1f040553770cf2e142c039495ff040.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/ad1f040553770cf2e142c039495ff040.webm?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/ad1f040553770cf2e142c039495ff040.mp4?t=1692380437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682380/extras/e656fec65a32ff948b9013c4f030f3e6.poster.avif?t=1692380437\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://s